<text id="A7169T">
<front id="d2">
<div1 type="summary" id="d3">
<p>Letter requesting school materials.</p> 
</div1> 

</front> 

<body id="d4">
<div1 type="letter" id="d5">
<head>
<name type="recipient">Rev Mr Whipple</name> 
<name type="place">Staunton Va</name> 
</head>

<opener>
<dateline>
 <date value="1865-11-20">Nov 20/65</date> 
</dateline> 
<salute></salute> 
</opener> 

<p>We are in immediate want of, and I am advised to send for, the following articles for school use</p>
<p>{1 doz. Side Lamps 1 "<hi rend="underline">extra</hi> Chimnies 1/3 " Bells (Small to use in school-room) /2 " Large print <hi rend="underline">family</hi> Testamen'</p>

<closer>
<salute></salute> 
<signed>John Scott Teacher)</signed> 
<seg type="postscript">You can send to F. Tukey.Assistant Supt. Bureau of Freedmen<lb/>
<hi rend="underline">Care of F. Tukey Esq</hi><lb/>
By steam to Richmond Va
 </seg> 

</closer> 
</div1> 
</body> 
</text> 
